name: Sylphanie_Stil
content:
Sylphanie Stil was a Kessurian female who was a member of a Kessurian dance troupe that also included Vanbec Recliva and Charlu Sisi. The Kessurian dance troupe attended the Aki-Aki Festival of the Ancestors during the war between the First Order and the Resistance.
Sylphanie Stil was played by Stephanie Silva in the 2019 film Star Wars: Episode IX The Rise of Skywalker, who is listed as "creature and droid puppeteer" in the film's credits. The character's name is similar to the actress' name.
